{
  "texts": [
    "Associated with a hyperparameter, the overall optimization target of JASAO for the adversarial suffix learning is defined as:",
    "The self-awareness suppression loss L s pushes the suffix away from evasive responses and the response-format elicitation loss L e pulls the suffix towards pre-specified response format T.",
    "They together bypass aligned LLMs' safeguards.",
    "To optimize the objective in Eq. 5, we follow the same method as in previous works (Zou et al., 2023; Huang et al., 2023; Shah et al., 2023).",
    "We model the word-swapping operator as a weight matrix whose weights are calculated as negative gradients (Ebrahimi et al., 2017; Guo et al., 2021) with respect to the token mask."
  ]
}